{"tid":724520,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺所有廢老都會有嘅習慣","createTime":"2018-07-01T03:47:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T07:47:08.000Z","uid":53619,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fc60ab3d444e0bfeea8a10d7534f79c0e5d82441","tid":724520,"uid":53619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T03:47:53.000Z","msg":"就係企係到老奉等人開門呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嘩賤到呢<br />\n見到有門就專登回頭望有冇人<br />\n一見有人行緊過嚟就施施然企埋邊<br />\n等人幫佢開門<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好啦，門開咗啦<br />\n唔該都冇聲就第一個「娟」入去<br />\n試過無數次都係咁，慶過火屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有手有腳係咪連道門都開唔撚到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲老人家行動不便拎住拐杖篤篤篤就算啦<br />\n但唔少廢老仲鬼咁生猛係到搏後生仔同情，好反感呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n於是我今日落去食個早餐<br />\n我跟係個廢老後面行<br />\n個廢老施施縮縮咁慢慢行去道商場門<br />\n仲時不時兩頭望咁<br />\n明明十幾步路程佢專登拖慢幾倍嚟行<br />\n我梗係知佢想點啦<br />\n於是我行快幾步去打開道門<br />\n正當對門比我打開一個身位時<br />\n個廢老已經想上前「娟」入去<br />\n我早佢一步先攝一隻腳落去，唔比佢過嚟<br />\n再成個身攝入去，然後光速關埋對門實一實<br />\n<br />\n班廢老開個門有冇咁難呀<br />\n平時是咪搭2蚊車搭出特權呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似咩都老奉咁，憨鳩鳩"},{"pid":"cdd56f41a4678629161c537505d53a2523cec2a9","tid":724520,"uid":69083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T03:58:28.000Z","msg":"有時屋苑都係 等人開門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我做人好撚有手尾<br />\n趁佢想入個時即刻關門"},{"pid":"9df5db2b8d4b7311887bd38a943f61d6352c0a25","tid":724520,"uid":53619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdd56f41a4678629161c537505d53a2523cec2a9","tid":724520,"uid":69083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T03:58:28.000Z","msg":"有時屋苑都係 等人開門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我做人好撚有手尾<br />\n趁佢想入個時即刻關門"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T04:00:23.000Z","msg":"呢啲咪態度正確囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0f5ed90033c1f648531840abc782e39ed760963","tid":724520,"uid":31758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T04:01:24.000Z","msg":"平時我行商場出入口 如果有兩度門既過 廢老係左邊等我開門 我會行去右邊開到勁細夠自己過再閂門"},{"pid":"5d63b1f53e949a0d8d353a572d433c56240b7884","tid":724520,"uid":102132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T04:01:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"646834125c94804f6c65e56f7f1bf2c30b72db85","tid":724520,"uid":186914,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T04:01:45.000Z","msg":"佢哋共同嘅位就係仆街<br />\n<br />\n呢班廢老淨係自私，仆街，黑心<br />\n<br />\n如果有purge ， 一定要purge呢班正仆街冚家剷"},{"pid":"eaa2ca15f4348114407b05bd2677d5b59697a9eb","tid":724520,"uid":53619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0f5ed90033c1f648531840abc782e39ed760963","tid":724520,"uid":31758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T04:01:24.000Z","msg":"平時我行商場出入口 如果有兩度門既過 廢老係左邊等我開門 我會行去右邊開到勁細夠自己過再閂門"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T04:05:02.000Z","msg":"試過，比佢屌翻轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1860bc45c0c8f3440db9e1e1f7037c78f011ac07","tid":724520,"uid":33982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T07:05:28.000Z","msg":"做得好呀ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38eca31831ace57e1904a64e5f80318b515c71e2","tid":724520,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T07:35:06.000Z","msg":"走果陣果陣拖多下拖到關門<br />\n<br />\n1999sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a10f8fd49904049f2d44a94c030e58ced17d9fd0","tid":724520,"uid":41963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T07:47:08.000Z","msg":"香港人大部份係咁<br />\n廢中廢老比例最多<br />\n最火既係<br />\n我出佢入或者掉轉<br />\n我開門然後佢迎面攝入黎<br />\n而家我有你冇你一開門就一個排雲掌打出去幫自己開路"}]}